他可能正在探测该岛的防御工事。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 02:30:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-arrests-former-chinese-navy-captain-whose-speedboat-entered-taipei-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>美国媒体和官员称，四名美国教育工作者在中国东北公园被刺伤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/four-american-educators-stabbed-park-northeast-china-says-us-media-officials-2024-06-11/</link><description>据美国媒体和美国政府官员称，据报道，来自爱荷华州一所小型大学的四名美国教育工作者周末在中国东北吉林省的一个公园内被刺伤。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 02:21:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/four-american-educators-stabbed-park-northeast-china-says-us-media-officials-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>韩国周末在边境入侵后鸣枪警告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-fired-warning-shots-weekend-after-border-incursion-2024-06-11/</link><description>韩国军方表示，最近因平壤向韩国发射运载垃圾的气球而导致紧张局势升级，一些朝鲜士兵短暂越过边境后，韩国军方在周末鸣枪示警。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 02:13:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-fired-warning-shots-weekend-after-border-incursion-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>关键通胀测试前美元坚挺，美联储预测更新</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firm-ahead-key-inflation-test-fed-forecast-update-2024-06-11/</link><description>周二，美元兑欧元徘徊在一个月高点附近，兑日元升至一周高点，交易员为第二天关键的美国通胀数据和美联储新利率预测做好准备。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 01:24:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firm-ahead-key-inflation-test-fed-forecast-update-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>在中国，对身份的追求推动了高端运动服饰品牌 Lululemon 的发展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-search-identity-boosts-lululemon-premium-sportswear-brands-2024-06-11/</link><description>高端运动服饰品牌在中国正享受着强劲的增长，因为它们开始直接吸引主要客户，这给大品牌耐克和阿迪达斯在价值 550 亿美元的运动服饰市场与本土竞争对手的竞争中带来了又一次挫折。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 01:03:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-search-identity-boosts-lululemon-premium-sportswear-brands-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>总统表示，菲律宾必须做好应对外部威胁增长的准备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-must-prepare-external-threat-now-more-worrisome-president-says-2024-06-11/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯表示，由于印太地区紧张局势加剧，外部威胁更加明显，菲律宾应该为任何可能发生的情况做好准备。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 00:00:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-must-prepare-external-threat-now-more-worrisome-president-says-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>独家：行业官员表示，越南多年来首次允许企业进口黄金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/vietnam-let-companies-import-gold-first-time-years-industry-official-says-2024-06-10/</link><description>一位行业官员告诉路透社，越南预计将在十多年来首次允许企业进口黄金，其目的是缩小当地价格与国际基准之间不断扩大的差距。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 23:35:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/vietnam-let-companies-import-gold-first-time-years-industry-official-says-2024-06-10/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：等待游戏，日本骚动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-10/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 21:47:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-10/</guid></item><item><title>加拿大法官下月辞去香港最高上诉法院职务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/canadian-judge-quit-hong-kong-top-appeals-court-next-month-2024-06-10/</link><description>香港最高上诉法院的一名加拿大法官周一宣布，她将于下个月任期届满后辞职，并表示她仍然对法院成员及其独立性充满信心。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 17:54:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/canadian-judge-quit-hong-kong-top-appeals-court-next-month-2024-06-10/</guid></item><item><title>英国法官称香港法治“严重受损”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-rule-law-profoundly-compromised-says-british-judge-2024-06-10/</link><description>一名上周从香港最高上诉法院辞职的英国法官周一表示，在政府持有强烈意见的领域，香港的法治受到严重损害。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 16:25:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-rule-law-profoundly-compromised-says-british-judge-2024-06-10/</guid></item><item><title>美国参议院小组扩大对宝马使用被禁中国供应商零部件的调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/us-senate-panel-expands-probe-into-bmw-use-parts-banned-chinese-supplier-2024-06-10/</link><description>参议院财政委员会主席周一表示，他正在扩大对德国汽车制造商宝马使用来自被禁中国供应商的电子元件的调查。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 14:29:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/us-senate-panel-expands-probe-into-bmw-use-parts-banned-chinese-supplier-2024-06-10/</guid></item><item><title>古巴吸引俄罗斯人和中国人重振陷入困境的旅游业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/cuba-woos-russians-chinese-revive-ailing-tourist-sector-2024-06-10/</link><description>一个工作日的早晨，俄罗斯游客谢尔盖·博亚里什尼奇 (Serguei Boyaryshnic) 带着家人带着敬畏之心在哈瓦那旧城色彩柔和的建筑和鹅卵石街道中漫步。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 11:08:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/cuba-woos-russians-chinese-revive-ailing-tourist-sector-2024-06-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>